{"title":"Hexo Instructions","uid":"f984699155b83aa2788288ed319191b9","slug":"Hexo-Instructions","date":"2022-12-02T14:24:59.000Z","updated":"2022-12-02T20:09:57.610Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Hexo-Instructions.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://miro.medium.com/max/1200/1*zGn8GFhpCNdbO3wSvJO2JQ.jpeg","content":"<h2 id=\"Quick-Start\"><a href=\"#Quick-Start\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Quick Start\"></a>Quick Start</h2><p>Create a new post</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">hexo new &quot;My New Post&quot;</code></pre>\n\n<p>Create a draft which will not be published</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">hexo new draft &quot;My New Draft&quot;</code></pre>\n\n<p>You can simply use <code>hexo new &#39;title&#39;</code> to create a new file.</p>\n<p>The default type of this file can be changed in <code>_config.yml</code>.</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-yaml\" data-language=\"yaml\"><code class=\"language-yaml\"># Writing\nnew_post_name: :title.md # File name of new posts\ndefault_layout: draft</code></pre>\n\n<h2 id=\"Tag-Plugins\"><a href=\"#Tag-Plugins\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Tag Plugins\"></a>Tag Plugins</h2><p><a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/tag-plugins\">Documentation</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"Code-Block\"><a href=\"#Code-Block\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Code Block\"></a>Code Block</h3><pre class=\"line-numbers language-javascript\" data-language=\"javascript\" data-start=\"1\" data-line=\"\" data-line-offset=\"0\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">alert(&quot;Hello World!&quot;);\nvar a &#x3D; &quot;hello&quot;;</code></pre>\n\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-python\" data-language=\"python\"><div class=\"caption\"><span>python</span></div><code class=\"language-python\">def hello():\n    print(&quot;Hello World!&quot;)</code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"Blockquote\"><a href=\"#Blockquote\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Blockquote\"></a>Blockquote</h3><blockquote><p>Hello World !</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"Youtube-Video\"><a href=\"#Youtube-Video\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Youtube Video\"></a>Youtube Video</h3><div class=\"video-container\"><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/hY7m5jjJ9mM\" frameborder=\"0\" loading=\"lazy\" allowfullscreen></iframe></div>\n\n<h3 id=\"Pullquote\"><a href=\"#Pullquote\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Pullquote\"></a>Pullquote</h3><blockquote class=\"pullquote\"><p>content</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"Jsfiddle\"><a href=\"#Jsfiddle\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Jsfiddle\"></a>Jsfiddle</h3><pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">&#123;% jsfiddle shorttag [tabs] [skin] [width] [height] %&#125;</code></pre>\n<iframe scrolling=\"no\" width=\"100%\" height=\"300\" src=\"https://jsfiddle.net/zhou6140919/jhw1f0gL/3/embedded/js,html,css,result/dark\" frameborder=\"0\" loading=\"lazy\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n<h3 id=\"Include-Posts\"><a href=\"#Include-Posts\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Include Posts\"></a>Include Posts</h3><pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">&#123;% post_path filename %&#125;\n&#123;% post_link filename [title] [escape] %&#125;</code></pre>\n<a href=\"/post/hello-world/\" title=\"I was Born!\">I was Born!</a>\n","feature":true,"text":"Quick StartCreate a new post hexo new &quot;My New Post&quot; Create a draft which will not be published hexo new draft &quot;My New Draft&q...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":758,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"frontend","slug":"frontend","count":1,"path":"api/categories/frontend.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"hexo","slug":"hexo","count":1,"path":"api/tags/hexo.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Quick-Start\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Quick Start</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Tag-Pl